---
import Base from '../layouts/Base.astro';
---

<Base
  title="Privacy Policy | Happy House"
  description="Happy House privacy policy. How we collect, use, and protect your information."
>
  <section class="bg-white py-24">
    <div class="mx-auto max-w-[800px] px-6">
      <h1 class="mb-8 text-[40px] font-bold text-navy">Privacy Policy</h1>
      <p class="mb-6 text-sm text-muted">Last updated: March 2026</p>

      <div class="space-y-6 text-muted leading-relaxed">
        <div>
          <h2 class="mb-3 text-xl font-bold text-navy">Information We Collect</h2>
          <p>When you submit a form on our website, we collect the information you provide, including your name, business name, email address, phone number, and website URL. We use this information to conduct your free market audit and to communicate with you about our services.</p>
        </div>

        <div>
          <h2 class="mb-3 text-xl font-bold text-navy">How We Use Your Information</h2>
          <p>We use the information you provide to deliver the services you've requested, including market audits and SEO consulting. We do not sell your information to third parties.</p>
        </div>

        <div>
          <h2 class="mb-3 text-xl font-bold text-navy">Cookies and Analytics</h2>
          <p>We may use cookies and analytics tools to understand how visitors use our website. This helps us improve our content and user experience.</p>
        </div>

        <div>
          <h2 class="mb-3 text-xl font-bold text-navy">Contact</h2>
          <p>If you have questions about this privacy policy, please contact us at hello@happyhouseseo.com.</p>
        </div>

        <p class="text-sm text-muted italic">[This is a placeholder privacy policy. Replace with your legally reviewed privacy policy before launch.]</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
</Base>
